  "detailed_description": "This video introduces a practical solution for preventing medication errors: reusable yellow bands that fit onto prescription bottles. It demonstrates how users can easily write the medication's name on the band using an included marker, enhancing readability for individuals with vision impairments. The video also highlights the product's reusability by showing how the writing can be effortlessly wiped away with an alcohol swab, and showcases two different sizes to accommodate various bottle types. The overall message emphasizes improved safety and ease of medication identification through this simple yet effective product.",
